description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if anyone mentioned in the 2024 Epstein documents is indicted on charges related to their relationship with Jeffrey Epstein between Jan 10 and March 31, 2024 ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

Note: if there are further releases of Epstein documents before the resolution date, they will count for this market. 

For the purposes of this market any indictment from the US Federal Government, State Government, District of Columbia and any county, municipality, or other subdivision of a State will count for this market.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from the US government, however a consensus of credible sources will also be used.
